n the middle east africa central and eastern europe the eurasian countries india and russia hervé joined xerox in 9 as a sales representative in paris he held positions of increasing responsibilities in sales and marketing for the company’s affiliate in france as well as other management roles of head of xerox operations in central and eastern europe israel and turkey president of xerox’s affiliate in brazil and chief operating officer of xerox dmo regions west covering latin america and the caribbean he holds a master’s degree in law from paris assas university he is a board member of a better chance a national nonprofit organization that recruits academically talented and motivated students of color and guides them toward a variety of educational and leadership opportunities related links download photo quick links our company citizenship innovation investor relations newsroom xrx hervé tessler insider trades for xerox corp bulletin investor alert expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close expand keep open close xerox corp nyse xrx go set alerts find a broker join td ameritrade market index overview profile news charts financials historical quotes analyst estimates options sec filings insiders marketstatecountryus xerox corp after hours  quotes are delayed by  min jul    pm xrx quoteszigman9composite   change   volume volume  quotes are delayed by  min quoteszigman9composite todays close     change   day low day high    week low  week high 4 4 insider activity individual hervé tessler mr hervé tessler is presidentcorporate operations  senior vp at xerox corp he is on the board of directors at a better chance inc he received his graduate degree from pantheonassas university transactions date shares transaction value copyright  factset research systems inc all rights reserved source factset fundamentals officers and executives mr jeffrey jacobson chief executive officer  director mr hervé tessler presidentinternationa